---
import MainLayout from '@layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About Me" description="Bassim Shahidy's personal website">
  <div>
    <section class="card-mx card-p mt-8 max-w-3xl">
      <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold">About Me</h3>
      <div
        slot="content"
        class="text-muted-foreground [&_a]:prose [&_a]:prose-neutral dark:[&_a]:prose-invert space-y-4">
        <p>
          Based in SF, I'm a software engineer and open source developer
          obsessed with building tools that solve meaningful problems and push
          the craft forward. I live for writing code that feels beautiful â€”
          thoughtful interfaces, smart design, and tools that just work.
        </p>
        <p class="">
          I'm building
          <a
            href="https://github.com/AVGVSTVS96/react-shiki"
            class="dark:hover:text-accent-300 hover:text-accent-400"
            >react-shiki</a
          >, a fast and flexible client-focused syntax highlighter for React. It
          provides a clean component API like
          <a
            href="https://github.com/react-syntax-highlighter/react-syntax-highlighter"
            class="dark:hover:text-accent-300 hover:text-accent-400"
            >react-syntax-highlighter</a
          >, alongside a more flexible React hook, bringing the modern, powerful
          <a
            href="https://github.com/shikijs/shiki"
            class="dark:hover:text-accent-300 hover:text-accent-400">Shiki</a
          >
          syntax highlighter to React in an elegant and intuitive package.
          <p>
            I'm also a Founding Engineer at
            <a
              href="https://github.com/assistant-ui/assistant-ui"
              class="dark:hover:text-accent-300 hover:text-accent-400"
              >assistant-ui</a
            >, where we're raising the bar for developer experience (DX) and
            accessibility in AI chat. It's a powerful SDK paired with a
            shadcn-style UI library, giving you everything you need to spin up
            an advanced, type-safe chat app with best-in-class design,
            accessibility, and performance. From a production-grade app in
            minutes to the most advanced workflows you can imagine, assistant-ui
            covers the full spectrum with a clean, composable API and
            exceptional DX.
          </p>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold">About This Website</h3>
        <div slot="content" class="text-muted-foreground">
          <p>
            This is website is built with Astro, Tailwind CSS, and React. It
            serves as my portfolio website, showcasing my technical skills, blog
            posts, and projects, while also acting as a sandbox to try things
            and add new features as I continue to learn and grow as a software
            developer.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
